Some are masters of the heavens above; others, caretakers & helpmates of the earth below—watchful eyes and ears throughout recorded history and beyond! Over the years, countless varieties of Pokémon have developed, and researchers have discovered hundreds of different types, but many more are yet to be discovered! Try and count them if you dare, but then—try and count the grains of sand on your favorite beach. We may never truly know their full extent, but one thing is certain—every Pokémon expresses life uniquely!

Today, there are people who collect Pokémon and train hard, striving for their dreams and ambitions. They embark on grand journeys, full of excitement, but full of challenges too. Being a trainer requires dedication and spirit! It is a long and difficult road, but those who travel it oft find friends along the way.

Together humans and Pokémon carry on, facing new challenges and sharing new adventures that will become the tales of tomorrow—but even tomorrow’s stories may have started long ago…

