Hello! And welcome to our RP! We're a group of RPers who've recently migrated onto RPNation and are looking to open the doors to some new members!

This RP draws from the extended Poké-Verse. What does that mean? It means we use a combination of canons: Main Series Games, side games, Anime, Manga, etc. Now, among all these canons we use the [div=display: inline; font-weight: bold; font-variant: small-caps; text-decoration: underline; color: green;]Main Series Games[/div] primarily, so we're game-primacy and the events of the main series games are considered to have been historical for the purposes of the RP, and all other canons are used in a supplementary fashion; they provide extensive world-building, locations, technology, etc.

The RP is designed to be a sandbox where characters can explore all the wonders of pokémon and RPers can nerd out over our beloved franchise.[/div]
